nmero se desplom cuando llegaron los Grimer.

Some say the reason Garbodor in Alola are a

Es frisst Mll und verdaut ihn in seinem Inneren

Mangia spazzatura e la trasforma in un veleno

Due to Gigantamax energy, this Pokmons toxic

This Pokmon eats trash, which turns into poison

Al entrar en contacto con el gas txico que emite

El veneno lquido que brota de su brazo derecho

I gas tossici che emette dalla bocca e dalle dita

It sprays toxic gas from its mouth and fingers. If
the gas engulfs you, the toxins will seep in all the

The toxic liquid it launches from its right arm
is so virulent that it can kill a weakened
creature instantly.
